  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, I-- I find out this was in the Royal Apollo Hotel, on a terrace, a [NON-ENGLISH], we call it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's one of the main thoroughfare in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the way there, as we turned maybe a-- a block, you know, not even a block, a drunken Russian soldier stand there, with a Katyusha, a little machine gun.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told us, [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, at the time, already shed the German uniform, naturally, even the shoes and everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I put on everything, my own clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we go to this Russian soldier, who was obviously drunk as a skunk, because [LAUGHS] you just went close to him, you get drunk by being next to him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, [RUSSIAN], which mean to come here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he tried to herd us in to a yard, in an apartment house yard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there were, next door to an apartment houses, four, five, six, story apartment houses, each had a little inside yard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we tried to tell him, you know, that we are with the resistance movement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried to show him the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when I find out that he was Wallenberg, because he said, I am Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm a Swedish diplomat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wanted to go to the embassy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the soldier just took our papers and tore it in million pieces and put them in the snow, which was that high at the time, and herd us-- us in, into this yard.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
